metadata.name: Heart
metadata.description:
Edition 1 of 1

3496 x 4500px, JPG  
Photographed using a NIKON D850 with a TAMRON SP 24-70mm F2.8 lens.  
The physical artwork is The physical artwork is 420 x 594 mm (16.5 x 23.3 in). It is made with gold ink on 270 gsm black A2 paper.

This artwork was created using a custom handbuilt drawing machine. I create each piece by carefully adjusting the speed of three motors and other settings. Each piece is unique.

The physical artwork will be sent to the first buyer of the NFT.
